Package model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Booking
    holds information about a particular booking
    Cinema
    Class to create Cinemas in Cineplexes and initialize shows in it
    Cineplex
    Cineplex master class
    master
    Master class to serve as the primary backend layer for the UI
    movie
    This class contains all the attributes of a movie and initializes the show class object to create a new show for the movie.
    MovieGoer
    movie-goer class which holds all the information about him/her including all the bookings made by them.
    MovieTicket
    Generate a Movie Ticket price
    PasswordHasher
    Hash Passwords using SHA1
    show
    This class uses the objects from the movie.java class to create shows for the movie in different cinemaplexes and screens
    TicketPrice
    Used to read all ticket prices from prices.txt
    TransactionID
    Generate Transaction ID for each Movie Ticket booking
